headline: FICO UK Credit Card Market Report: October 2024
summary: LONDON, December 18, 2024--Following expected seasonal trends between summer and Christmas, October 2024 saw sales and credit card balances drop, month-on-month according to data from global analytics software leader FICO. However, the high cost of living that has been a feature of 2024 means spending remained 1% higher than the same period in 2023.
